xwax (1.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release
  * Remove patch that was merged upstream in 1.6 final release
  * Font package name has changed, avoid pulling in transitional package
  * Bump debhelper compatibility version
  * Use https for Vcs fields in control file
  * Update Debian readme with current script name and wiki link
  * Enable all security hardening options
  * Enable parallel build
  * Update copyright notice
  * Improve format of watch file to sort betas correctly
  * Add myself to the list of uploaders

